<span id="supportus"></span><div id="divhow" class="supportus">    <h2 class="h2reverse">We need your Support</h2>    <p style="text-align: center; font-size:18px; max-width:600px; margin: 0px auto;">Together we can change the way we discover research. We are a non-profit organisation run by a dedicated group of volunteers, eager to shape Open Knowledge Maps with you! Here's how you can help:</p>       <div class="howitworks-div">                 <div class="howitworks-point">            <span>                <p>                    <span class="number"><i class="fa fa-commenting-o" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>                </p>                 <p><strong>Let us know what you think.</strong>                    In order to improve our Open Knowledge Maps, we need your feedback.                    Write us an <a class="underline" href="mailto:info@openknowledgemaps.org">E-Mail</a>                     or post issues on <a class="underline" href="https://github.com/OpenKnowledgeMaps" target="_blank">Github</a>.                </p>            </span>        </div>        <div class="howitworks-point">            <span>                <p>                    <span class="number"><i class="fa fa-share-alt" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>                </p>                <p><strong>Share your favourite maps with others.</strong>                    We have a new sharing feature, which lets you easily share your favourite maps with the world.                     Spread the word as far as you can.                </p>            </span>        </div>        <div class="howitworks-point">            <span>                <p>                    <span class="number"><i class="fa fa-users" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>                </p>                <p><strong>Tell your friends and colleagues about us.</strong>                    Do you know someone who could benefit from Open Knowledge Maps? Tell them about us!                </p>                <div class="a2a_kit a2a_kit_size_32 a2a_default_style">                    <div class="sharebutton"><a class="a2a_button_twitter"></a></div>                    <div class="sharebutton"><a class="a2a_button_facebook"></a></div>                    <div class="sharebutton"><a class="a2a_button_email"></a></div>                    <div class="sharebutton"><a class="a2a_dd" href="https://www.addtoany.com/share"></a></div>                </div>                <script async src="https://static.addtoany.com/menu/page.js"></script>            </span>        </div>            </div>        <p style="display: block; margin:0px auto; text-align:center;"><a style=" text-align: center;" class="newsletter" href="getintouch">Get in touch</a>    </p></div><script type="text/javascript">    $(document).ready(function() {        if(window.location.hash.length > 0 && typeof $(window.location.hash).offset() !== "undefined") {            window.scrollTo(0, $(window.location.hash).offset().top);        }    });</script>